The 3D NPC provides an extra dimension to achieve full QPM and nonlinear beam shaping simultaneously39–41. By using the femtosecond laser erasing technique, one can engineer the amplitude of the nonlinear coefficient d33 in a LiNbO3 crystal, which is modulated to (1−v) d33 in the laser illuminated area35,38. Here, v is defined as the modulation depth. The 3D distribution of χ(2) in the nonlinear crystal is written as1\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
